title: 106: The Aldi Haul Episode: June '20 Edition
itunes:title: The Aldi Haul Episode: June '20 Edition
description: In this episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are opening up their taste buds to 9 GREAT finds from the Trader Joe’s sister store, ALDI! Finds like flatbreads, 45-calorie multi-grain bread, cashew crisps, vegan meatballs, veggie burgers, and SO MUCH MORE. Plus, an AMAZING fiber-ific bar and frozen sushi that’s surprisingly REALLY GOOD! Did we mention it was also Lisa’s first time ever inside ALDI? What are you waiting for?! Push play, and then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products mentioned in the episode.
itunes:summary: The hauls keep on coming… This time we’re going to ALDI!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
